{"tid":1098289,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"Hongkongers: Endgame","createTime":"2019-04-09T03:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T02:01:38.000Z","uid":234362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffdc9fd195f3d06aea37f1d209ab6928455fa5a","tid":1098289,"uid":234362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"它拿起金色手套，彈指之間，大家身上都染上一片片紅。人人開始化為灰塵，包括那些為社會付出的、願為人民福祉而忍辱負重的、為民主公義而發聲的、還有很多很多⋯⋯他們有部份從社會的目光中消失，被鎖在靈魂牢獄裡。<br />\n<br />\n       社會中不乏不知情的人，當中亦不少得高學歷人士。博士在步入牢獄之際，鋼鐵俠問他：&rdquo;Why are you doing this?&rdquo; 博士告之：&rdquo;We are in the Endgame now.&rdquo; 博士清楚知道，在過千萬個可能之中，只有一個能把我們引向勝利。就算致勝的機會微不足道，只要Hongkongers 能從失敗的陰霾中走出來，共同抵抗握有北極強權的它，那麼，之前的，都稱不上是失敗。<br />\n<br />\n       如今，那些人已經灰飛煙滅。只不過，他們並沒有死去。他們的離去，正為Hongkongers 蘊釀最後一波反擊，重拾昔日香港的光輝。<br />\n<br />\n       面對著9位的離開， Some people move on, but not us...... not us......<br />\n<br />\n       晨曦將再次出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDeep Purple - Love Conquers All<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zWD_cuKKCAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzWD_cuKKCAM&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLQjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=c4486d67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zWD_cuKKCAM</a>"},{"pid":"9168f650adb8502d64b15ce123ca188adedb9f02","tid":1098289,"uid":234362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01573eb7b2469d07e35fad52753137ab5fdf8b11","tid":1098289,"uid":219179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab360ef97a67ad7261bcfb6e778e5613629b887","tid":1098289,"uid":234362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d59fb9675ad7a7c7ee8b0edee9ac833123f5e1dd","tid":1098289,"uid":234362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"推"